]]\n* {{nowrap|{{Flagicon image|Flag of Catalonia.svg}} [[Generalitat de Catalunya]]}}\n* {{nowrap|{{Flagicon image|Flag of the Basque Country.svg}} [[Euzko Gudarostea]]{{efn|From 1936 until it surrendered in 1937 to the Italian [[Corpo Truppe Volontarie]] in the [[Santo\u00f1a Agreement]].|name=\"Basque\"}}}}\n* {{nowrap|{{Flagicon image|Flag of the International Brigades.svg}} [[International Brigades]]}}\n{{plainlist|\n* '''Supported by:'''\n* {{flag|Soviet Union|1936}}\n* {{flag|Mexico|1934}}\n* {{flagdeco|France|1830}} [[Third French Republic|France]] <small>(1936)</small>\n* [[Foreign involvement in the Spanish Civil War#International volunteers|Foreign volunteers]]\n}}\n| combatant2  = {{Flagdeco|Spain|1938|size=30px}} '''[[Nationalist faction (Spanish Civil War)|Nationalists]]'''\n* {{nowrap|{{Flagicon image|Bandera FE JONS.svg}} [[Falange Espa\u00f1ola Tradicionalista y de las Juntas de Ofensiva Nacional Sindicalista|FET y de las JONS]]{{efn|The only party under [[Francisco Franco]] from 1937 onward, a [[Unification Decree (Spain, 1937)|merger of the other factions on the Nationalist side]].|name=\"FetJons\"}}}}\n* {{nowrap|{{Flagicon image|Bandera FE JONS.svg}} [[Falange Espa\u00f1ola de las JONS|FE de las JONS]]{{efn|1936\u20131937, then merged into [[Falange Espa\u00f1ola Tradicionalista y de las Juntas de Ofensiva Nacional Sindicalista|FET y de las JONS]]|name=\"Natmerge\"}}}}\n* {{flagicon image|Flag of Traditionalist Requetes.svg}} [[Requet\u00e9s]]/[[Traditionalist Communion|CT]]{{efn|1936\u20131937, then merged into [[Falange Espa\u00f1ola Tradicionalista y de las Juntas de Ofensiva Nacional Sindicalista|FET y de las JONS]]|name=\"Natmerge\"}}\n* {{flagicon image|CEDA flag.svg}} [[Spanish Confederation of Autonomous Right-wing Groups|CEDA]]{{efn|1936\u20131937, then merged into [[Falange Espa\u00f1ola Tradicionalista y de las Juntas de Ofensiva Nacional Sindicalista|FET y de las JONS]]|name=\"Natmerge\"}}\n* {{nowrap|{{flagicon image|Bandera de Reno